Type of Feat: Class
Prerequisite: Crusader Level 1.
Specifics: You learn and ready maneuvers as a Crusader.

Use: Selecting this feat places your personal copy of the Book of the Nine Swords in your inventory.

If you already have this item selecting this feat will turn turn the martial adept menu for this class on and off.

When you are ready to level you may also select this feat out of combat to bring up a selection of new maneuvers to learn.